%% Editable Mermaid source for the end-to-end data flow.
%% Render: https://mermaid.live  or  `mmdc -i data_flow.mmd -o data_flow.png`
flowchart LR
    subgraph Brokers
      A[Broker Alpha · CSV]
      B[Broker Beta · JSON]
      C[Broker Gamma · pipe-delimited]
    end

    A & B & C -->|native formats| K{{Apache Kafka}}
    K -->|insurance.policies.raw| SS[Snowpipe Streaming client]
    K -->|insurance.claims.raw| SS

    SS --> RAW[(RAW · VARIANT)]
    RAW -->|sp_raw_to_staging + Cortex header mapping| STG[(STAGING · canonical)]
    STG -->|sp_run_data_quality| GOV[(GOVERNANCE · DQ audit)]
    STG -->|sp_cortex_enrichment| STG
    STG -->|sp_staging_to_analytics| AN[(ANALYTICS · star schema)]
    AN -->|sp_anomaly_detection| AN
    AN --> SEM[(SEMANTIC · business views)]
    SEM --> DASH[Streamlit Dashboard]
    SEM --> AGENT[AI Agent · NL to SQL]
    GOV --> DASH
